Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.34,0:00:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在無限的時間裡一切都停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.84,0:00:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類孤獨的燃燒著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.14,0:00:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都沒有注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.84,0:00:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界偏離了軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.30,0:00:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被紅世的火焰包圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.75,0:01:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使總有一天會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我現在卻是如假包換的坂井悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使總有一天會被遺忘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.54,0:02:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的存在之力也留給了小池他們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.11,0:02:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此我覺得很滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.03,0:02:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情也變得很平淡輕鬆了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.45,0:02:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來是打算自己領悟的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.91,0:02:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我什麼也不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.47,0:02:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切才只不過剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.59,0:02:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和夏娜的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.75,0:02:28.74,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(340,315}迷茫的弗來姆黑茲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.58,0:02:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...咖啡勺子...還有..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.42,0:02:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個聖火的燭火明明快要熄滅了的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.25,0:02:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然恢復了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.65,0:02:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？不可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.88,0:02:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  可能是寄宿在他體內的寶器造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會..寶器是..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.16,0:02:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:00.20,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,註釋："紅世之徒"秘寶中的秘寶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零時迷子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一時間我也很難相信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.17,0:03:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能..那個居然在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.17,0:03:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.81,0:03:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就更不能交給那個獵人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.11,0:03:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好先看看情況再說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.10,0:03:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.08,0:03:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明擺著嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.97,0:03:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去屋裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.33,0:03:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進屋？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.39,0:03:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯   不然你會被淋濕的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我覺得你要盯著我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.43,0:03:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是待在我身邊比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.06,0:03:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得累嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.22,0:03:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不著裝模作樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.14,0:03:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有裝模作樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.87,0:03:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是...不明白為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗來姆黑茲對天氣什麼的不在乎的...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要進屋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽睡在一樓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.97,0:04:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不弄出很大聲就沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.65,0:04:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就睡那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.28,0:04:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去爸爸的書房睡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了盯著你才進屋的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.63,0:04:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼還要去別的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.81,0:04:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.94,0:04:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己說出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.89,0:04:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就在這兒睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.80,0:04:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...你要幹嘛呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.86,0:04:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是換衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.32,0:04:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀...但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.48,0:04:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個...可是地點...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.60,0:04:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好慌的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.33,0:04:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所介意的事是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找個地方躲起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是偷看就把你踢飛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣....
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.42,0:04:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.25,0:04:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要催我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  真意外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:04:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.10,0:05:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然會害羞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡衣...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.06,0:05:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你不要偷看的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒偷看...只不過問你有沒有帶睡衣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.11,0:05:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.35,0:05:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有內衣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.18,0:05:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為身體上的污垢「阿拉斯托爾」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.25,0:05:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用火炎就可以清除
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.10,0:05:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過換了會比較舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.92,0:05:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？真方便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,床左邊的抽屜裡有浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.70,0:05:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來   你沒帶行李呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.66,0:05:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大致的用品都裝在裡面了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.47,0:05:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.26,0:05:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不多不少
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在弗來姆黑茲的黑衣裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.29,0:05:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直跟魔法一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.10,0:05:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿拉斯托爾的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊  阿拉斯托爾是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.82,0:05:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.40,0:06:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是紅世之王中的一個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.51,0:06:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...和那個吞噬存在之力的紅世之徒一樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有光憑慾望去吞噬存在的傢伙存在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.44,0:06:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有像我們一樣殲滅他們的人存在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"存在之力"不在紅世
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而在這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.72,0:06:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此"徒"就被吸引來到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.35,0:06:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了掌握存在之力來滿足自己的各種慾望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.60,0:06:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些徒是從哪裡來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.28,0:06:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅世啊    無法從這裡跨過去的相鄰世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像「異次元」樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.21,0:06:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣理解也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.61,0:06:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果他們得到了存在之力的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.86,0:06:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晚會破壞這個世界和紅世的平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了阻止那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會有我們這樣的弗來姆黑茲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說我們就是說你們還有同伴咯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.07,0:06:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有其它的弗來姆黑茲  但沒有同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.96,0:06:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人戰鬥的理由和手段都不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.93,0:07:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候弗來姆黑茲之間也會發生戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.28,0:07:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟有些暴躁的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.68,0:07:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得合作的話比較有效率
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.36,0:07:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小悠  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.22,0:07:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  整理下房間而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  已經很晚了適當點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  還差十拳就可以收拾他了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.59,0:07:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是聖火
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.24,0:07:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在意志和鬼面前裸體有什麼不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.83,0:07:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何況還是你....
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正就是討厭那樣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  弗來姆黑茲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了「弗利阿古內」而來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.44,0:08:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此  若已經被我們先得到的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該就會靜靜地離開的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.14,0:08:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗來姆黑茲即使相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.73,0:08:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是各自為政呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好的房間空著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.63,0:08:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.46,0:09:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼   這就是所謂這個城市最好的房間？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是感謝得快要流淚了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.73,0:09:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總比你去勾引男人得到的小巢好不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.59,0:09:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的"花癡公主"瑪喬裡·鐸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.30,0:09:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我閉嘴  白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.74,0:09:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.85,0:09:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到逃到這種城市裡來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.99,0:09:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運屍者那個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.24,0:09:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡有徒了  就只有弗來姆黑茲而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.36,0:09:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連聖火都是搞得七零八落的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.64,0:09:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托你的福  害我難以察覺那傢伙的行蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.34,0:09:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.17,0:09:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說那個徒被弗來姆黑茲給燒成灰啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.71,0:09:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許吧  反正這裡是糟糕透了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.32,0:09:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種小玩意算什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.12,0:09:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘是些便宜貨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.73,0:09:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是最好的酒店啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.64,0:10:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為讓你今晚沒有好酒喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.31,0:10:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然察覺到了  是弗來姆黑茲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.49,0:10:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜  已經沒時間去顧米斯特斯了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.11,0:10:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.26,0:10:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了天壤劫火的弗來姆黑茲外又來了一個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您小心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.18,0:10:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的   瑪麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.37,0:10:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待會兒再去為你收集一些能量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.75,0:10:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到現在就不能讓他們來妨礙我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.42,0:10:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要這個計劃成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.55,0:10:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不用再做"麟子"那種道具了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是作為一個存在生存在這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.72,0:10:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人  我現在已經很滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.51,0:10:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有我給你力量  不出三天你就會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.13,0:10:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是非常虛幻的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.43,0:10:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得 那就是和主人間的不可分割的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.66,0:10:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗亞   瑪麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.44,0:10:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的話多麼令人愉快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.49,0:11:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.79,0:11:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無論如何都要實現
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.59,0:11:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從紅世來到這裡的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.53,0:11:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個世界追求存在的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.96,0:11:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是為了你   瑪麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.31,0:11:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多好美麗的景色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.38,0:11:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.12,0:11:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在之力有這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.96,0:11:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.43,0:11:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  肯定會順利的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.84,0:11:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我小睡一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.61,0:11:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個地方的確不適合休息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.13,0:11:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是下去怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.28,0:11:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.14,0:12:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好香啊 軟軟的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.35,0:12:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呀 原來是夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.43,0:12:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？為什麼.....
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.88,0:12:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.01,0:12:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼她會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你該介意的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是介意什麼....
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.99,0:12:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.07,0:12:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等...不...我完全什麼都....
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.64,0:13:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不記得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.12,0:13:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我勸你到下面來睡的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.71,0:13:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為看你有點累了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.58,0:13:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡得迷迷糊糊地就跑到床上去的是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.16,0:13:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是平常的你的話....
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.63,0:13:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯....沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.81,0:13:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是聖火
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.37,0:13:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個問題？？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.04,0:13:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了煩死了煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.63,0:13:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.61,0:13:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之還得上學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.84,0:13:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快換衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.38,0:13:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去洗了臉再來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.65,0:13:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.15,0:13:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎....好不錯呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡相好可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.58,0:13:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.54,0:13:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  給我加把勁跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.38,0:13:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呀  近滕這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙地有氣勢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.09,0:14:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從以前開始就是個怪人不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.83,0:14:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還色色的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.09,0:14:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的  在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.93,0:14:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井那傢伙....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼囂張地把老師當白癡耍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.72,0:14:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的課上可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.94,0:14:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會好好重新鍛煉你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呀  這是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.53,0:14:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分明是為難我們呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.04,0:14:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是....這樣好像不會和老師起衝突了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.13,0:14:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡   平井那傢伙還很爽的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.76,0:14:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.59,0:14:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是單純的魔鬼訓練嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒力氣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.75,0:14:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.83,0:14:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.92,0:14:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你們在幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.10,0:14:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師請讓一美休息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.06,0:15:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有貧血症
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說這種話就是想偷懶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.20,0:15:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在怎麼花時間體力也不會增強的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.98,0:15:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師...住手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.65,0:15:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼樣都太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.65,0:15:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.79,0:15:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師這是為了鍛煉你們....
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.80,0:15:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礙著我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.15,0:15:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.03,0:15:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻不拉嘰的訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.59,0:15:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了勞累什麼意義也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.41,0:15:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  給我解釋下這課的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.37,0:15:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼...你...平井你踹老師會怎麼樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.08,0:15:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.34,0:15:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.65,0:15:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很成問題的行為呀...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.69,0:15:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停課...不對...退學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礙眼的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那是什麼表情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜那傢伙不會又打老師吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.72,0:15:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我說...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.58,0:15:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井那傢伙 要打架了 幫把手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.56,0:15:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.66,0:15:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是阻止她也是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.20,0:15:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂...平井...你聽到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:15:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踢腿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.27,0:16:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.47,0:16:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師...沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.45,0:16:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危險的哦 突然跑到跑道上去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧...大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.19,0:16:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對...對...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.53,0:16:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.89,0:16:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也看到了...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.10,0:16:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為平井的跑得很快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.95,0:16:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是交通事故呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.56,0:16:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.84,0:16:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微威脅下他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.33,0:16:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡單點就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.93,0:16:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛好在跑道上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.84,0:16:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師...今後不當心的話可危險了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.11,0:16:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以解散了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.41,0:16:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是自習....
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.59,0:16:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你們喜歡好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.25,0:16:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井你什麼時候想到那辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.10,0:16:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.76,0:16:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了一口氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行得很順利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.41,0:17:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是這樣想的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.45,0:17:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜當時抱著什麼樣的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.81,0:17:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想像不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來想打他的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.63,0:17:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踢腿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.42,0:17:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是想誇他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.08,0:17:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可那個指示真是絕妙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.17,0:17:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是沒那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是會毫不猶豫地揍了那老師...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.75,0:17:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍稍會吃點苦頭的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.52,0:17:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...怎麼會...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.73,0:17:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼   為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.98,0:17:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說為什麼對聖火那麼焦躁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.15,0:17:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白   不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.56,0:17:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉...已經焦躁不堪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.78,0:17:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徒和弗來姆黑茲的氣息都混在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.44,0:17:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「運屍者」在哪裡都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:17:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是你所希望的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.99,0:17:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得不錯   搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.74,0:18:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛好深入的調查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.09,0:18:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣好嗎  要插同行的隊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.09,0:18:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳出去可不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.96,0:18:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些小細節我才不管呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.51,0:18:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意見的話就一下解決他算了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.41,0:18:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備完畢  隨時都可以開始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了馬太 馬可 裡加
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.39,0:18:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四散各處
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.71,0:18:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將眼前美夢破壞的妖怪聽我吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.02,0:18:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子並不是路過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.91,0:18:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該已經察覺到我們的意圖了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.70,0:18:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個範圍振動的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.35,0:18:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「自在法」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.51,0:18:41.10,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,註釋:"紅世之徒"與弗來姆黑茲自由操作"存在之力"\N所引起的種種現象的總稱。
